"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-c94b1b91b91c9c6266f3c301bb8406e0_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1413 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447545640"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIwcS3lsiytsZYEAMaCDYxNzMzMjA1IJbugYIGMAY4vwRAB3IJNDQ3NTQ1NjQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1615197700.2290678", "card_id": "Q_448183082", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 368}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待政协委员建议婚恋教育设为大学必修课？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "全国政协委员于欣伟呼吁，构建和完善高校婚恋教育体系。她建议，打造以学校教育为主体、家庭教育辅助、社会教育影响的三维婚恋教育模式，将婚恋教育设为高校学生必修课。你怎么看？（中国教育报）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-dae11a96fbf7b8cdb99e4057fee5fc76_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1411 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/448183082"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIwcS3lsiytsZYEAMaCDYxODc1MTM2IPznlYIGMBo4zgdACHIJNDQ4MTgzMDgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1615197700.229543", "card_id": "Q_447939211", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1398}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全国人大代表建议春节假期延长至 10 天，你赞成吗？可行性如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据安徽商报，全国人大代表、肥东县总工会兼职副主席李小莉建议春节假期延长至 10 天，缓解交通压力。李小莉表示，春节期间大量人口集中出行，对交通、旅游资源和公共服务体系形成巨大挑战，超出资源对应的合理人口规模，安全隐患大大增加，交通拥堵让人苦不堪言，安全事故也会增多。若假期延长到 10 天左右的话，既可感受中国传统文化的氛围以及与家人团聚的温暖，也能缓冲一下交通等各方面压力。 全国人大代表：建议春节假期延长至 10 天｜两会聚焦 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5df4fd6b354c41c7a9dde73f01922510_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1411 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447939211"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIwcS3lsiytsZYEAMaCDYxODIw